FBIS3-58640 "drweu012_h_94007" FBIS-WEU-94-012 Document Type:Daily Report 19 Jan 1994 GERMANY Kohl Supports Call For Public Sector Pay Freeze LD1901131394 Berlin DDP/ADN in German 1240 GMT 19 Jan 94 LD1901131394 Berlin DDP/ADN Language: German Article Type:BFN [Text] Magdeburg (DDP/ADN) -- Chancellor Helmut Kohl has supported the call by Interior Minister Manfred Kanther for a pay freeze in the public sector. It is impossible to move outside the general development of the economy, the chancellor said at a news conference in Magdeburg today. Kohl declined to give figures for his expectations for the pay and conditions round. Securing jobs has priority, he said.
